SplitCodeBoard layout and wiring notes

Matrix overview
- Left half: 5 rows x 6 cols
- Right half: 5 rows x 6 cols
- Main split total: 5 rows x 12 cols
- Missing keys: use NONE (no physical switch)

Diode and scan direction
- Per-switch wiring pattern: COLx -> switch -> diode -> ROWy
- ZMK diode-direction for this pattern: col2row

ZMK sizing and offsets
- rows = 5
- columns = 12
- right col-offset = 6
- macropad col-offset = 12 (left + right)

