Active key count
- Left: 28 keys
- Right: 28 keys
- Main split total: 56 keys

Transform/keymap rule
- Include only physical keys in transform and keymap.
- Do not include NONE positions.


SDA and SCL refer to SDA and SCL on the MCP23017, SDA on the nrf52840 is P0.04 and SCL on the nrf52840 is P0.05 
SDA and SCL are connected on right and left.

COL0 > P0.03
COL1 > P0.28
COL2 > P0.29
COL3 > GPB3
COL4 > GPB4
COL5 > P1.11
ROW0 > P1.15
ROW1 > P1.14
ROW2 > P1.13
ROW3 > P1.12
ROW4 > P0.10

Right rotary encoder wiring
- A > GPB1
- B > GPB2
- S1 > GPB5
- C is grounded
- S2 is grounded

